{"tid":1101131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽歌舞團　巨聲震沙田","createTime":"2019-04-11T00:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T11:46:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"73862e96895519c10377c803a9e8bdbdd32ee506","tid":1101131,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=ef9cb1be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田城門河畔近年「歌聲飄揚」，疑有在屯門公園「搵食」的大媽歌舞團最近加入進駐，日日沿岸放聲高歌，吸引大批大叔圍觀。歌女演唱期間收受大叔打賞，更疑設「卡拉OK」服務，大叔付費點唱或自娛高歌，大媽記帳後私下收費。惟激昂歌聲滋擾沿岸居民及跑步人士，即使掛滿針對噪音的警告橫額，區議員仍接獲投訴不絕，直斥執法少、檢控程序繁瑣，建議倣效亂拋垃圾般即時票控。<br />\n<br />\n東網記者連日觀察，沙田公園對出的瀝源橋附近，數隊歌舞團長駐表演。上周四下午約3時，1名長髮歌女在橋底下獨唱，連接喇叭及咪高鋒，高唱多首國語經典，至少10名大叔圍觀，有老伯更豪爽地拿出100港元鈔票打賞。她一直演唱至黃昏近6時，期間有單車人士疑不滿她聲浪過大，舉起手機拍攝。該處近年不少大媽跳舞，近日此類疑來自屯門公園的大媽歌舞團入侵，聲威更壯。<br />\n<br />\n沿河岸旁掛起多幅橫額，列明在公眾地方奏玩任何樂器或使用揚聲器，最高可罰款1萬港元。惟警告作用不大，同日不遠處就有另一班歌女載歌載舞，中年女士放聲高歌，逾10名街坊跳舞，途經市民均要再三退避。<br />\n<br />\n假期更熱鬧，河邊3、4個歌舞團大比併，其中1隊歌舞團有歌女身穿華麗禮服，由下午2時許開始高歌，時而獨奏、時而合唱。除了數名成員輪流獻唱外，亦有疑似街坊即席演唱，及後成員以筆記簿或平板電腦記錄。據了解，成員為演唱者記帳，表演街坊每首點唱歌曲需付30港元。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區區議員丘文俊指，雖沿岸有警告列明製造噪音可被罰款，近年接獲噪音滋擾投訴卻不跌反升，他指目前檢控程序繁瑣，過去更鮮有執法。他指遠至車公廟站屋苑居民投訴噪音滋擾，建議當局倣效票控亂拋垃圾的做法即時票控。<br />\n<br />\n同區另一區議員黎梓恩亦指，近2年收到逾40宗噪音投訴，他認為掛橫額警告作用有限，又指歌舞團已由原來2至3檔，擴展至5至6檔，反映當局未能有效打擊。<br />\n<br />\n執業大律師陸偉雄稱，以《噪音管制條例》檢控必須要有人投訴，經執法部門搜證，投訴人出庭作證才有機會成功檢控，他擔心改成票控將面對法律挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人指，由2017年至今年第1季，共接獲299宗涉及沙田城門河畔行人路一帶的噪音投訴，並在去年4月向一名人士提出檢控，該人士被法庭判處罰款3000港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=5b664d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=da432814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=eb5b1f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_05b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=6a7e7a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_06b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=3260d36c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_07b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=b345b64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_08b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=5050bd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_09b.jpg?20190411050407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20190411050407&h=d175d8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fbkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=ef44418b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/bkn-20190411050036868-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"38c139068c40fa2af09f2e9453474d928be5bbb8","tid":1101131,"uid":799,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:18:15.000Z","msg":"廢老禍港"},{"pid":"a90fc70a5b203dfb4b436515f6162ca3f4645619","tid":1101131,"uid":7323,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"愈來愈多呢d，周圍都有<br />\n唱歌，跳舞<br />\n好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"63cdb50313222022d949ebbe65ebe373e5b7e894","tid":1101131,"uid":152701,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"好波<br />\n反正入來呢個post<br />\n講埋啲咩「死廢老」/「支那狗」果班傻西<br />\n都係得個講字 叫佢地最簡單上街遊行佢地都懶<br />\n最好再多十幾廿團<br />\n反正支那港豬都無撚用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f207efc141ad1268b031c9ab3c585f71ee197ec6","tid":1101131,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a90fc70a5b203dfb4b436515f6162ca3f4645619","tid":1101131,"uid":7323,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"愈來愈多呢d，周圍都有<br />\n唱歌，跳舞<br />\n好撚嘔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:43:36.000Z","msg":"連我d討厭政治既親戚都開始覺得有問題<br />\n乜乜公園廣場都開始多大媽團佔據"},{"pid":"b6ada859cb49d859006cca5af7fab59dc5e607a4","tid":1101131,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:46:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4e513997807da7b90c18faf9364c3b6b107e322","tid":1101131,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6ada859cb49d859006cca5af7fab59dc5e607a4","tid":1101131,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:46:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:49:29.000Z","msg":"駐屯門夜夜笙歌 檢控繁複變相縱容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/photo/bkn-20190411045904267-0411_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190411050409\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190411045904267-0411_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190411050409&h=c58c03bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門公園及土瓜灣海心公園是大媽歌舞團長期表演區，過往即使地區人士及傳媒多番踢爆她們收錢唱歌，甚至疑涉色情交易，又有被判罰款的案例，仍無阻大媽夜夜笙歌。有地區人士坦言，屯門公園的滋擾情況毫無改善，現時檢控方式繁複，且不接受康文署外判保安作證人，變相縱容該批人士繼續製造聲浪。<br />\n<br />\n「我唔覺得有改善過喎，佢哋冇錢收又點會繼續唱落去！」屯門區議員龍瑞卿指，屯門公園的大媽唱歌及收取利是情況並無間斷，現時康文署雖有聘用外判保安負責監察，惟當局提出檢控時，需要有人作證，但法庭卻不接受保安作為證人，須由其他人指證，致檢控難度甚高亦不合理，她認為該做法是間接縱容大媽多年來噪音滋擾，促當局簡化檢控程序。<br />\n<br />\n其實，市民要一展歌喉，坊間供唱歌的場所不少，國際標準舞資深導師曹智成指，現時政府的社區中心都開放予團體申請使用，只要透過區議員或註冊團體可以免費使用場地獻唱，中心設有良好的隔音設備以及音響器材，亦可參加有專業導師指導的跳舞班，結識志同道合的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/bkn-20190411045904267-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190411%2Fbkn-20190411045904267-0411_00822_001.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=7e1944e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190411/bkn-20190411045904267-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"58e0309e1cbd7261c3d0bd65799825bf858a130e","tid":1101131,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"